Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你“死”了\N{\rEng}You failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有\N{\rEng}I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,枪在我手里\N{\rEng}The gun is in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为我拿到了\N{\rEng}I thought I had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 父亲 我下次一定可以的\N{\rEng}Sorry, Father. I'll make it next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,千万不要认为你拥有的一切是理所当然的\N{\rEng}Never take anything for granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,否则上帝会夺走你所拥有的\N{\rEng}God will take it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝是坏蛋吗\N{\rEng}Is God bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝很公平\N{\rEng}God is fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你差点就抓到我了 对吗 小家伙\N{\rEng}You almost got me, didn't you, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我的白发是从你那里遗传来的吗\N{\rEng}Did I get my white hair from you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还是从妈妈那里\N{\rEng}or from Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈遗传给你的\N{\rEng}From your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信我们连她的照片都没有\N{\rEng}I can't believe we don't have any pictures of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,照片什么的都在大火中被烧毁了\N{\rEng}Everything was destroyed in the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的\N{\rEng}You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时只能救出你\N{\rEng}I could only save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,她漂亮吗\N{\rEng}Was she beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她很聪明\N{\rEng}She was smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.42,0:04:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就像你一样\N{\rEng}Like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我做对了多少\N{\rEng}How many did I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:04:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,全对了\N{\rEng}All of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那我今天可以进城了 对吧\N{\rEng}So I get to go to town today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,实战中你输了\N{\rEng}You failed survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,已经三个月了\N{\rEng}It's been three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,况且 我刚刚还给你剪了一个很棒的发型\N{\rEng}Plus, I just gave you a killer haircut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,请相信我\N{\rEng}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须先通过所有的测试才行\N{\rEng}You need to pass all your tests first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 除了些常见的\N{\rEng}All right, apart from the usual,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我还订购了五种蕨类植物\N{\rEng}I have an order of five ferns,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,两种榕属植物\N{\rEng}two ficuses,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还有大圆柱藻\N{\rEng}and the Columnea grandiosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,格洛里奥萨\N{\rEng}Gloriosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,格洛里奥萨\N{\rEng}Gloriosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天能带小凤去吗\N{\rEng}Am I taking Phoenix today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不行\N{\rEng}Not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,已经有一段时间没去了\N{\rEng}It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了 不行\N{\rEng}I said, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你对她管的越严\N{\rEng}You either loosen up that leash,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,越容易适得其反\N{\rEng}or sooner or later, she's gonna bite it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,跟赫尔南德斯一起去吧\N{\rEng}Go with Hernandez.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,记得日落前回来\N{\rEng}Back by sunset!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 赫尔南德斯\N{\rEng}Hey, Hernandez.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 小美女\N{\rEng}Hey, gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真好听\N{\rEng}That's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你自己编的曲子吗\N{\rEng}You made that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我小的时候妈妈唱给我听的\N{\rEng}I think my mom sang it to me when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我只记得前面部分\N{\rEng}That first part's all I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你想去祭拜一下她吗\N{\rEng}You wanna pay her a visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,-但是我父亲不想让我去 -只要你不说 我绝对不会说的\N{\rEng}But my father doesn't want me--I won't tell if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,警方已对托马斯·汉尼曼博士发出全州警报\N{\rEng}REPORTER Police have issued a statewide alert for Dr. Thomas Hanniman,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,此人在底特律地区\N{\rEng}who's believed to be running an organ trafficking ring
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 组织经营器官贩运 -谢谢\N{\rEng}in the Detroit area.Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,其绑架数量惊人\N{\rEng}The alarming number of abductions
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,且数量近期在该市更是有所上升\N{\rEng}has recently risen in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,更多消息静待通报 我们会即时向您通报最新情况\N{\rEng}This is a developing story. We'll update you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,将更多信息公之于众\N{\rEng}as more information comes to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们来看周末的天气预报\N{\rEng}Now let's take a look at the weekend forecast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,大家早上好 我是气象学家杰瑞\N{\rEng}JERRY Good morning, everyone. I'm meteorologist Jerry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来帮个忙\N{\rEng}Everyone, pull. Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿卡住了\N{\rEng}It's stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.87,0:08:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 要试点好玩的吗\N{\rEng}Hey, wanna try something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:08:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\rEng}Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,再快点 再快点\N{\rEng}Faster, faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点晕了\N{\rEng}I'm getting dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 伙计们 进来吃饭了\N{\rEng}Hey, guys. Come on in. Dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想进去\N{\rEng}But I don't wanna go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.17,0:09:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 伙计们\N{\rEng}Come on, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,“圣约人庇护所”\N{\rEng}"Covenant Shelter."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我跑的比你快\N{\rEng}Race you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.48,0:09:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 等等\N{\rEng}Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-玩得开心吗 -嗯嗯\N{\rEng}You having fun?Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我们走吧\N{\rEng}All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去小便\N{\rEng}I need to pee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 那就快点\N{\rEng}Okay, well, be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不敢惹毛你父亲\N{\rEng}I don't wanna anger your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 你真漂亮\N{\rEng}Wow, you're pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字 小美女\N{\rEng}What's your name, gorgeous?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫雷兰\N{\rEng}Mine's Raylan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我无关\N{\rEng}I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了 我父亲在等我\N{\rEng}I need to go. My father's waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我打个响指\N{\rEng}I snap my fingers
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他能把你的蛋蛋给咬下来\N{\rEng}and he'll bite your testicles off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哇\N{\rEng}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我吓到你了 我很抱歉\N{\rEng}Well, I'm sorry if I scared you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我才没被你吓到\N{\rEng}Who said you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,回头见\N{\rEng}I'll see you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 小影\N{\rEng}Come on, Shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\rEng}You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,遇到个怪人\N{\rEng}Just a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这附近怪人很多\N{\rEng}No shortage of those around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,跟上他们\N{\rEng}Follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 赫尔南德斯\N{\rEng}Thanks, Hernandez.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今天玩得很开心\N{\rEng}We had a lot of fun today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不介意的话 我下周再带她去\N{\rEng}I'll take her again next week if you're okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:11:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今天玩够了吧\N{\rEng}Today was enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-虽然这跟我无关 但是 -你说得对\N{\rEng}It's none of my business, but--You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,本来就跟你无关\N{\rEng}It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得你是个坏人\N{\rEng}You're a bad man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,做过一些坏事的恶棍\N{\rEng}A man who's done terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你是这么想的\N{\rEng}At least, I know you think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我有时候也觉得自己很坏\N{\rEng}Just like sometimes I do about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.18,0:12:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,战争改变了我们所有人\N{\rEng}War changes us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,战后没有谁的灵魂还是圣洁的\N{\rEng}No soul returns holy from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不应该让她跟你一样承受这些\N{\rEng}Don't make her pay for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你能把你的车子挪开吗\N{\rEng}You mind moving your vehicle off the road, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…\N{\rEng}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是回镇上的唯一一条路\N{\rEng}This is the only road back to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你当过兵吗\N{\rEng}You served?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.59,0:14:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都当过兵\N{\rEng}We all did too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,参加过伊拉克战争吗 -是的\N{\rEng}Iraq? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,从一场不光彩的战争中不光彩地退伍\N{\rEng}Dishonorably discharged from a dishonorable war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不知道为什么 我却感觉很光荣 你呢\N{\rEng}I'd say that makes us honorable somehow. Wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不光荣\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在能把你的车从路上挪开了吗\N{\rEng}Can you move your truck off the road now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.66,0:14:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以 宝贝\N{\rEng}Sure, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你想怎么都可以\N{\rEng}Whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,下个月的课程\N{\rEng}Lessons next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我明年想去上学\N{\rEng}I wanna go to school next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-在家就能上学 -我想上一所真正的学校\N{\rEng}This is school--A real school,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,和其他像我一样大的孩子在一起上学\N{\rEng}with other kids like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在家上学更安全\N{\rEng}Homeschool is safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想要安全\N{\rEng}I don't wanna be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我想做个正常人 我想交朋友\N{\rEng}I wanna be normal. I wanna have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-我想过一种… -够了\N{\rEng}I wanna live a--Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,够了\N{\rEng}Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经失去过一个女儿了\N{\rEng}I already lost a daughter once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能再失去你\N{\rEng}I'm not losing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我很孤独\N{\rEng}But I'm lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不知道孤独是什么滋味\N{\rEng}You have no idea what it is to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.03,0:16:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你起码还有我呢\N{\rEng}You have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有你根本不够\N{\rEng}You're not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,“圣约人庇护所\N{\rEng}"Covenant Shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你的新家正等着你呢”\N{\rEng}Your new home awaits you."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小影\N{\rEng}Shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,小影\N{\rEng}Shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.30,0:24:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,小影\N{\rEng}Shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.70,0:24:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\rEng}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.87,0:26:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快拿盒子\N{\rEng}The box! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.00,0:26:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\rEng}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.98,0:27:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,去抓住那个女孩\N{\rEng}Go get the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.91,0:27:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,开门\N{\rEng}Open the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.65,0:27:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,开门\N{\rEng}Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.23,0:30:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的怎么回事？\N{\rEng}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.58,0:30:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,噢！\N{\rEng}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.80,0:30:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住 兄弟\N{\rEng}Hang on, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.86,0:30:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,张嘴\N{\rEng}Open your jaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.64,0:30:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,忍住\N{\rEng}Stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.48,0:30:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸 兄弟\N{\rEng}Breathe, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.84,0:30:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙是海豹突击队员\N{\rEng}The guy's a Navy SEAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.82,0:31:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的海豹突击队 兄弟\N{\rEng}Fucking dead SEAL, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.88,0:32:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好离开那里 孩子\N{\rEng}Better get out of there, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.59,0:32:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他下来了\N{\rEng}He's down there with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.11,0:32:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那该死的瞎子就在下面\N{\rEng}Blind fuck is down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.35,0:32:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,打电话给雷兰\N{\rEng}Call Raylan.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.30,0:33:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,金属盒子里面灌满了水\N{\rEng}Metal box is almost full of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.26,0:33:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是希望孩子活着…\N{\rEng}You prefer to see the kid alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.57,0:33:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就到这里来\N{\rEng}you come in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.10,0:33:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我在跟你开玩笑吗\N{\rEng}You think I'm fucking with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.19,0:33:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.63,0:33:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有一根带电的电线快要通到水里了\N{\rEng}There's a live wire about to reach the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.11,0:33:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,快出来 不然她就完蛋了\N{\rEng}Come out, or she's fried!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.61,0:34:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,真他妈的聪明\N{\rEng}Clever fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.00,0:34:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没枪吧\N{\rEng}No guns, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.70,0:34:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题\N{\rEng}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.73,0:36:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是个硬汉\N{\rEng}You're tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.42,0:36:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你完蛋了\N{\rEng}But you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.96,0:37:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的怎么回事？\N{\rEng}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.22,0:37:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,喔  老兄\N{\rEng}Yo, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.78,0:38:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,深呼吸\N{\rEng}Breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.83,0:38:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 深呼吸\N{\rEng}Come on, breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.17,0:38:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,深呼吸\N{\rEng}Breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.18,0:38:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,深呼吸\N{\rEng}Breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.45,0:38:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是那个老瞎子干的吗\N{\rEng}The old blind man did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.88,0:38:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯\N{\rEng}Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.28,0:38:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\rEng}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.08,0:39:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以走\N{\rEng}I can walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.82,0:39:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了 我可以走\N{\rEng}I said, I can walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.48,0:39:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了\N{\rEng}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.58,0:39:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,把守出口\N{\rEng}Cover the exits.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.11,0:39:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的怎么回事？\N{\rEng}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.66,0:40:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还在下面\N{\rEng}They're still down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.74,0:40:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了\N{\rEng}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.52,0:40:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是谁 -我不知道\N{\rEng}Who are they?I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.14,0:41:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不要害怕 小姑娘\N{\rEng}You don't need to be afraid, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.79,0:41:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切只是一个误会\N{\rEng}This has all just been one big misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.46,0:41:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该害怕的不是我\N{\rEng}It's not me you need to be scared of...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.16,0:42:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,而是站在你旁边的那个人\N{\rEng}but the man standing next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.30,0:42:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 我不知道他是谁\N{\rEng}Now, I don't know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.83,0:42:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道他不是什么好人\N{\rEng}But I know who he's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.40,0:42:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该告诉她还是告诉你\N{\rEng}Should I tell her or you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.15,0:42:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,干掉他 兄弟\N{\rEng}Finish him, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.07,0:42:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.89,0:42:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-爸爸 爸爸 醒醒 -你不是很厉害吗\N{\rEng}Dad! Dad, wake up.Aren't you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.46,0:42:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我！\N{\rEng}Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.73,0:42:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点\N{\rEng}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.90,0:42:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 没事的\N{\rEng}No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.86,0:42:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 就在这样\N{\rEng}Yeah, there you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.87,0:42:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这就对了\N{\rEng}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.26,0:42:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的不记得我了 是吗\N{\rEng}You really don't remember me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.92,0:42:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我就帮你回忆回忆\N{\rEng}Maybe this will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.28,0:43:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了吗？\N{\rEng}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.33,0:43:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEng}What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.46,0:43:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,几年前 我们的房子着火了\N{\rEng}Years ago, there was a fire in our house.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.42,0:43:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,警察将过错算在了我身上\N{\rEng}Cops blamed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.68,0:43:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我在监狱里呆了八年\N{\rEng}I spent eight years in prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.16,0:43:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我时刻都想着是否还能再见到你\N{\rEng}wondering if I'd ever see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.17,0:43:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至不知道你是死是活\N{\rEng}I didn't even know if you were dead or alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.39,0:43:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这个变态\N{\rEng}This creep here must have...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.18,0:43:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,一定是找到了你想把你占为己有\N{\rEng}found you and kept you for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.79,0:43:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来是本地新闻\N{\rEng}REPORTER Up next in local news,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.79,0:43:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,底特律西部的一家冰毒实验室今早着火\N{\rEng}a meth lab caught fire in west Detroit this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.93,0:43:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,警方逮捕了主要嫌疑人\N{\rEng}Police were able to arrest the primary suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.71,0:43:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,该男子已被拘留 可能面临指控\N{\rEng}The man was taken into custody and could face charges
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.72,0:43:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,其身犯数罪\N{\rEng}for a large number of crimes committed
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.63,0:44:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-在过去的几年里 -你不知道\N{\rEng}over the past several years.You have no idea
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.24,0:44:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我等这一刻有多久了\N{\rEng}how much I've been waiting for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.17,0:44:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他伤害过你吗\N{\rEng}Did he hurt you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.00,0:44:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但他确确实实把你从我身边抢走了\N{\rEng}But he did steal you away from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.66,0:44:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,现在他必须死 你明白吗\N{\rEng}and now he must die, you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.75,0:44:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了他\N{\rEng}Kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.49,0:44:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-不 -操 你在干什么\N{\rEng}No.Fuck are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.62,0:44:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不要在我孩子面前动手 在外面吧\N{\rEng}Not in front of my kid. Do it outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.85,0:44:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,醒醒 你这个该死的瞎子\N{\rEng}Wake up, you blind fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.81,0:44:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,噢！操！\N{\rEng}Oh! Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.09,0:45:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的混蛋\N{\rEng}Fucking coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.45,0:45:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,把她带到车上 我去追捕这个混蛋\N{\rEng}Take her to the truck while I hunt this motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.06,0:45:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\N{\rEng}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.42,0:45:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-放开我 -你怎么回事\N{\rEng}Let me go!What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.16,0:45:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不想回家吗\N{\rEng}Fucking wanna go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.79,0:45:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我不管你是谁\N{\rEng}I don't care who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.45,0:46:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我要教你一些该死的礼仪 哟\N{\rEng}I'm gonna teach you some fucking manners, yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.28,0:46:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个忘恩负义的贱人\N{\rEng}You ungrateful, little bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.04,0:46:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.39,0:46:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\rEng}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.31,0:46:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\rEng}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.27,0:46:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\rEng}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.11,0:46:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,行动 快\N{\rEng}Move. Go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.76,0:46:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,行动 快\N{\rEng}Move. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.66,0:47:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,快\N{\rEng}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.68,0:47:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 伙计\N{\rEng}I'm sorry, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.38,0:47:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-他回到屋里了 -我知道\N{\rEng}He's back in the house.I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.07,0:47:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他想让我们去追他\N{\rEng}He wants us to follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.38,0:47:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这些愚蠢的游戏真是玩够了\N{\rEng}Enough of these silly games.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.84,0:48:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他的夹克\N{\rEng}JIM- It's his jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.41,0:48:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好样的\N{\rEng}Attaboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.71,0:48:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好样的\N{\rEng}Attaboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.67,0:48:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\rEng}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.76,0:48:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,停下\N{\rEng}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.28,0:48:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的吗\N{\rEng}Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.68,0:48:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\rEng}Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.90,0:48:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我的真名是什么\N{\rEng}What's my real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.51,0:48:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧过来\N{\rEng}Get over here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.81,0:48:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我的生日是什么时候\N{\rEng}When's my birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.29,0:48:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,-我亲爸是谁 -闭嘴\N{\rEng}My real one?Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.29,0:48:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你才闭嘴\N{\rEng}No, you stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.26,0:48:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\rEng}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.33,0:49:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEng}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.41,0:51:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,小凤\N{\rEng}Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.24,0:51:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点 丫头\N{\rEng}Calm down, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.42,0:51:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静\N{\rEng}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.96,0:51:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,待着\N{\rEng}Stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.63,0:51:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,把她带到车上\N{\rEng}Put her in the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.70,0:52:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 哇…！\N{\rEng}Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.36,0:52:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛呢\N{\rEng}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.44,0:52:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-你的狗在里面  -狗死了\N{\rEng}Your dog's in there.Dog's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.01,0:52:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不一定\N{\rEng}You don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.71,0:52:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你想去看看吗\N{\rEng}You wanna go and find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.59,0:53:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.03,0:56:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 小公主\N{\rEng}Good morning, princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.17,0:56:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉怎么样\N{\rEng}How you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.57,0:56:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\rEng}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.70,0:56:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,想和我坐一起吗\N{\rEng}Wanna sit with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.88,0:56:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,来 坐我旁边来 来吧\N{\rEng}Come, sit with me. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.06,0:56:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.10,0:56:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这就对了\N{\rEng}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.76,0:56:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这就对了\N{\rEng}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.93,0:57:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.64,0:57:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,门是开着的\N{\rEng}Door's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.33,0:57:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你不再是囚犯了\N{\rEng}Not a prisoner anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.64,0:57:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说我可以走了\N{\rEng}You mean, I can go?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.08,0:57:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你愿意\N{\rEng}If you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.39,0:57:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,或者你可以留在这\N{\rEng}Or you can stay here
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.26,0:57:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,搞清楚你到底是谁\N{\rEng}and find out who you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.58,0:57:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我有兄弟姐妹吗\N{\rEng}Do I have any brothers or sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.23,0:57:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾 没有\N{\rEng}Unfortunately, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.50,0:57:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我的生日是什么时候\N{\rEng}When's my birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.50,0:57:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,2月20日\N{\rEng}February 20th.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.29,0:57:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我母亲叫什么名字\N{\rEng}What was my mother's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.25,0:57:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,约瑟芬\N{\rEng}Josephine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.90,0:57:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我长得像她吗\N{\rEng}Do I look like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.95,0:58:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.61,0:58:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你很像她\N{\rEng}You do.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.35,0:58:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,塔拉\N{\rEng}Tara.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.74,0:58:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的真名\N{\rEng}That's your real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.01,0:58:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,塔拉\N{\rEng}Tara.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.97,0:58:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人告诉你的一切都是谎言\N{\rEng}Everything that man told you is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.32,0:58:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么样了\N{\rEng}What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.23,0:58:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他得到了应有的惩罚\N{\rEng}He got what he deserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.80,0:58:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 我不觉得抱歉\N{\rEng}Hey. I'm not sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.89,0:58:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不应该害怕\N{\rEng}You shouldn't be either.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.94,0:58:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想离开\N{\rEng}I wanna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.51,0:58:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪里？你要去哪里\N{\rEng}Where? Where you gonna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.46,0:58:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道一个庇护所\N{\rEng}There's a shelter I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.03,0:58:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了\N{\rEng}Like I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.73,0:58:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你不再是囚犯了\N{\rEng}you're not a prisoner anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.71,1:01:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈？\N{\rEng}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.19,1:01:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,正如我所说…\N{\rEng}Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.67,1:01:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉你的一切都是谎言\N{\rEng}everything he told you was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.04,1:01:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我的小塔拉\N{\rEng}My Tara?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.43,1:01:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你…\N{\rEng}You...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.04,1:01:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,长这么大了\N{\rEng}got so big, heh.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.79,1:01:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以抱你吗\N{\rEng}Can I hug you?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.45,1:02:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,到这儿来\N{\rEng}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.37,1:02:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,哦天哪\N{\rEng}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.98,1:02:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\rEng}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.72,1:02:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\N{\rEng}Mmm. Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.55,1:02:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 宝贝 我们太想你了\N{\rEng}Oh, baby, we missed you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.17,1:02:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…\N{\rEng}Mmm...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.30,1:02:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你\N{\rEng}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.74,1:02:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你那时特别乖\N{\rEng}You were such a beautiful baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.40,1:02:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,拿出来\N{\rEng}Get it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.10,1:02:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,拿出来 快\N{\rEng}Get it out. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.63,1:02:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这就对了 这就对了\N{\rEng}There you go. There you go. There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.89,1:02:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,-抱歉 -没什么好道歉的\N{\rEng}Sorry.Nothing to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.29,1:02:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\rEng}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.16,1:03:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那场烧毁我们家的大火…\N{\rEng}The same fire that destroyed our family...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.47,1:03:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,烧坏了我的内脏\N{\rEng}it burned up my insides.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.87,1:03:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈和爸爸曾经…\N{\rEng}Mom and Dad used to have a...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.05,1:03:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有一个厨房（指制毒室）…\N{\rEng}kitchen, heh...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.79,1:03:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们房子的地下室里\N{\rEng}in the basement of our house,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.88,1:03:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们过去经常在那施展“厨艺”\N{\rEng}where we used to cook.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.71,1:03:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,当然那是为了我们的生意\N{\rEng}It was for our business.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.24,1:03:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你渴吗\N{\rEng}Are you thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.39,1:03:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,塔拉\N{\rEng}Tara?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.48,1:03:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我快死了\N{\rEng}I'm dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.96,1:03:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEng}What?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.61,1:04:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那些化学品产生的烟雾…\N{\rEng}The smoke from the chemicals...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.96,1:04:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,毒害了我的血液 毒害了我的内脏\N{\rEng}poisoned my blood and badly damaged my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.75,1:04:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我时日无多了\N{\rEng}I don't think I have much time left.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.71,1:04:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么别的办法吗\N{\rEng}Is there anything you can do?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.15,1:04:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说你在我们的老房子给我种了些花\N{\rEng}I heard you left flowers for me at our old house.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.12,1:04:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的吗\N{\rEng}Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.38,1:04:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\rEng}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.65,1:04:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你是不是希望\N{\rEng}Weren't you wishing
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.91,1:04:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈能健康的活着呢\N{\rEng}your mama was healthy and alive?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.91,1:04:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.76,1:04:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要一颗新的心脏 宝贝\N{\rEng}I need a new heart, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.71,1:04:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但不是随便什么人的都可以\N{\rEng}But not just any heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.07,1:05:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,医生说一定得是 呃\N{\rEng}Doctor said it has to be a, uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.59,1:05:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那一定得是…\N{\rEng}It must be a...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.07,1:05:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我相容的器官捐赠者\N{\rEng}compatible donor.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.99,1:05:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,比如 直系亲属\N{\rEng}Like a direct relative.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.78,1:05:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你有着能救妈妈性命的东西\N{\rEng}You hold the gift that can save your mama's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.92,1:05:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 宝贝 我需要你把它作为礼物送给我\N{\rEng}And, baby, I need that gift.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.81,1:05:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那样我们就可以同呼吸共命运了\N{\rEng}We'll finally be together as one.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.81,1:05:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你会活在我的身体里\N{\rEng}You'll live on in me.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.59,1:06:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,回家\N{\rEng}Go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.00,1:08:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,走开\N{\rEng}Go away.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.18,1:08:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了 走\N{\rEng}I said, go.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.45,1:08:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,留下来\N{\rEng}Stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.67,1:08:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,留下来\N{\rEng}Stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.97,1:09:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,回家\N{\rEng}Go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.19,1:09:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,回家\N{\rEng}Go home.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.80,1:10:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能理解\N{\rEng}I hope you understand
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.15,1:10:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这个过程具有着高风险\N{\rEng}the high risks of this procedure.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.72,1:10:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我付你的钱够多了\N{\rEng}I think I pay you enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.37,1:10:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴 做好你的工作\N{\rEng}Shut up and do your job.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.77,1:10:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么她还活着\N{\rEng}Why is she still alive?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.95,1:10:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她死了 她的心脏也废了\N{\rEng}If she's dead, so is her heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.73,1:10:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能让心脏保鲜足够长的时间\N{\rEng}And I can't keep it fresh long enough
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.73,1:10:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有合适的设备\N{\rEng}without the proper equipment.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.00,1:10:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我得趁她还活着的时候把心脏取出来\N{\rEng}I have to cut it out of her while she's still breathing.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.05,1:10:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEng}JOSEPHINE Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.83,1:10:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 嘿\N{\rEng}Hey, hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.44,1:10:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿\N{\rEng}Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.49,1:10:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.34,1:11:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了 伙计\N{\rEng}JIM- What's wrong with you, man?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.69,1:11:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在里面做的那些事是不对的\N{\rEng}What they're doing in there is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.69,1:11:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我们的厨师\N{\rEng}She's our cook.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.57,1:11:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她死了 就没人给我们生产毒品了\N{\rEng}If she dies, there's no product.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.70,1:11:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没有毒品 我们也活不下去\N{\rEng}If there's no product, there's no us.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.57,1:11:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,懂了吗\N{\rEng}¿Comprende?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.01,1:11:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但那样做还是不对的\N{\rEng}Still fucking wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.85,1:11:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEng}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.42,1:11:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗 -嗯\N{\rEng}You ready? Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.42,1:11:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开始吧\N{\rEng}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.66,1:12:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他妈的怎么回事？\N{\rEng}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.76,1:12:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看\N{\rEng}Go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.03,1:12:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\rEng}Hm.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.75,1:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你杀了我兄弟\N{\rEng}You killed my brother!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.10,1:13:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个死瞎子\N{\rEng}You blind freak!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.43,1:14:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我要像剁南瓜一样剁开你的脑袋\N{\rEng}I'm gonna carve your fucking head open like a pumpkin, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.53,1:15:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为小影报的仇\N{\rEng}This is for Shadow.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.28,1:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 他妈的\N{\rEng}Oh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.84,1:15:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEng}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.94,1:15:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,就是他\N{\rEng}It's him.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.42,1:15:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 他怎么找到的\N{\rEng}How the hell did he find...?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.57,1:15:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的叛徒\N{\rEng}Disloyal fucking animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.66,1:15:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都还好吗\N{\rEng}Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.27,1:15:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 一切无恙\N{\rEng}Yeah, everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.67,1:15:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-没事的 我保证 -宝贝 我有点担心\N{\rEng}Everything's okay, I promise.Baby, should I be worried?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.72,1:15:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不用担心 完全不用\N{\rEng}No, no. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.46,1:15:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有我在呢\N{\rEng}I got you. I got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.98,1:15:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没有电 我没办法干活\N{\rEng}I can't work without power.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.63,1:15:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…\N{\rEng}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.68,1:16:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,计划有变\N{\rEng}Change of plans, then.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.38,1:16:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,收拾好你的东西 带上那女孩\N{\rEng}Pack your things. Bring the girl.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.34,1:16:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,劳尔\N{\rEng}Raul.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.30,1:16:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,带人过来 杀了那个瞎子\N{\rEng}Bring the men. Kill the blind man.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.95,1:16:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-带多少人 -全带上\N{\rEng}How many of us? All of you!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.52,1:16:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\rEng}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.79,1:17:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会杀了她的\N{\rEng}They're gonna kill her.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.10,1:17:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受不了\N{\rEng}And that's not cool with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.54,1:18:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他们现在要走了\N{\rEng}They're leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.89,1:18:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你身后的梯子\N{\rEng}The ladder behind you
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.20,1:18:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,直接通往他们那儿\N{\rEng}leads directly to them.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.85,1:18:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好快点\N{\rEng}You'd better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.47,1:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,左边\N{\rEng}Go left.
